------------------------------
Setup twitter-fetcher
------------------------------

Setup oauth tokens
==============================

* issue request tokens on youRoom

setup pit
  EDITOR=vi ./script/console
exe ./script/runnner ./script/maintenance/insert_attachment_template_for_twitter_fetcher.rb

* set tokens with pit
  EDITOR=vi ./script/console
    youroom request token and secret
    youroom access token and secret
    twitter request token and secret

Setup database
==============================

copy database.yml.sample to database.yml

rake db:create
rake db:migrate

Start service
==============================

Lunch service
